#### Start with Diffit, a tool specifically designed to differentiate text.
* #### Go to <a href="https://web.diffit.me/" target="_blank">Diffit</a>.
* #### Copy and paste a reading from a recent lesson plan or any news article.
* #### Choose the reading level to differentiate it to and/or language to translate it into.
* #### Click “Generate Resource”.

